Package org.molgenis.matrix

Package to deal with data in a matrix shaped format, such as phenotypes, genotypes, qtls, and so on.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Matrix<E> MOLGENIS interface to handle matrix like data sets: Its row and column dimensions have metadata attached on type and any other information the user would like to add.
 

Class Summary
CsvMatrix<E> Matrix that loads its data from a CsvReader.
MatrixDimension  
MemoryMatrix<E> Simple 'in-memory' implementation of the Matrix.
ObservedValueMatrix Naive implementation of a datbase backed matrix that will base its view (order) on what features and targets there are set to be selected.
 

Exception Summary
MatrixException
